OL,3,C81-year-old actress will perform nude
OL,4,Cin front of thousands
OL,6,FIllona Linthwaite, an actress and
OL,7,Fgrandmother, has just celebrated her
OL,8,F81st birthday and soon will be
OL,9,Fperforming at the Royal Opera House`
OL,10,Fwithout any clothes on for most of the
OL,11,Fshow.
OL,13,FShe wants to defy the "bad press"
OL,14,Fgiven to older women and "walk her own
OL,15,Fpath".
OL,17,FIlona will be playing Erda, the
OL,18,Fcharacter who represents nature, in a
OL,19,FWagner opera 'Siegfried', known as the
OL,20,F'Ring Cycle'.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
