OL,3,C81-year-old actress will perform nude
OL,4,Cin front of thousands
OL,6,FShe has performed from the age of 18
OL,7,Fbut this will be her first time
OL,8,Fappearing naked on stage. There will
OL,9,Fbe up to 2200 people in the audience
OL,10,Fevery night.
OL,12,FIlona says that she does not feel self-
OL,13,Fconscious when she is on stage and is
OL,14,F"looking forward to it". She said:
OL,16,F"The curtain goes up and there's
OL,17,Fnothing happening, it's just me.
OL,19,F"I thought that was really frightening
OL,20,Fand then when it happened, I thought,
OL,21,Factually, this is brilliant."
