OL,3,C81-year-old actress will perform nude
OL,4,Cin front of thousands
OL,6,FIlona spoke about when she was first
OL,7,Fasked to take on the role:
OL,9,F"I said, 'Why? Why are you asking me
OL,10,Fthis at my age?' I did have
OL,11,Ftrepidation, nerves and wondered why I
OL,12,Fwas letting myself do this,"
OL,14,FBut she wants to defy the usual
OL,15,Fattitudes around ageing and women.
OL,17,F"I don't care what people think now,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
OL,20,F"Actually, that's not quite true.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@\O]yD@AOUyD@eO]|D@AOU
