OL,3,C81-year-old actress will perform nude
OL,4,Cin front of thousands
OL,6,F"I was going to say I don't care what
OL,7,FI look like. I do care what I look
OL,8,Flike.
OL,10,F"On a certain level, I'm quite vain.
OL,11,FBut there is something about just
OL,12,Fowning yourself as you are."
OL,14,FThe actress says that she has not
OL,15,Falways felt positively about ageing,
OL,16,Fand remembers being 19 looking at a 28-
OL,17,Fyear-old drama student with pity.
OL,19,F"I thought, 'Oh dear, that's really
OL,20,Fhard to be that old and be among the
OL,21,Frest of us
